{
  "stem": "7455.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] The next morning, we did not go to work because we did not know if it's safe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Suddenly, even though we thought that our cellar, being so in the rear, that nobody knows, my brother [INAUDIBLE] is standing downstairs, and suddenly, from the window, he sees a rifle is being thrust in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thrust in.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a German said, get out!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get out!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother said, don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a Ukrainian policeman who was-- he told us he's collecting some-- gathering some people that they have to help to clean up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He did not say what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When we were up on that-- under the rooftop there, my brother had high temperature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had no aspirin, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So taking him would have been terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started begging.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we know men are in bigger danger than women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister and I said, take us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to go help clean up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hesitantly, he agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we are both walking, with my Laura-- my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he brings us to the area where our synagogue was, Beth Olam [INAUDIBLE] synagogue, and walks us in-- he leads us into that place, and he said, stay here until I get back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got used to the darkness, we saw bodies on the floor stretched out like-- like sardines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was frightening to be so close to a dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we saw there was-- in Brody, there was an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a husband and wife that they were-- there was the adopted fathers in charge, Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Okser.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very respectable people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And now we saw Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Okser shot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And her dress was up that you saw her thigh naked.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
